umor_com-medrectangle-4\"></span></p><h3>Pricing &amp; Availability</h3><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire.jpg\" alt=\"michelin pilot sx bmx racing tires\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-630x420.jpg 630w\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-297x198.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-800x533.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-120x80.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-768x512.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-696x464.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-1068x712.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/22100856/michelin-pilot-sx-bmx-race-tire-630x420.jpg 630w\"></a></p><p>The Michelin Pilot SX and Pilot SX Slick BMX Racing Line tires retail at £44.49 and £47.49, respectively. Pick them up now from Silverfish and other Michelin Bicycle retailers.</p><p><a href=\"https://motorcycle.michelinman.com/bicycle/home-bicycle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>Michelin.com</em></a></p></div></div>","author":"Jessie-May Morgan","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"eba90481b2232c585c5ce596835ed4dec58c0c89f761649a55e270661eb8fc34","category":"Cycling"}